{"tid":2487792,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來阿源鍾意一個女仔都等咗八年","createTime":"2021-04-13T23:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T07:32:13.000Z","uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9241dcc22782b8de222c31eefab3c53478bb1b5f","tid":2487792,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:18:40.000Z","msg":"篇文2013年<br />\n<br />\n阿源今日脫毒成功，真係成功需苦幹！佢由一位「覺得自己係零」嘅隱青，之後去咗港大圖書館做助理，雖然並唔係咩高薪厚職，總算踏實做人自強不息，間唔時仲去做義工，佢女朋友Fanny就係05年做義工時識嘅!<br />\n<br />\n今日有報道訪問阿源，究竟點樣追到拍拖5個月嘅女友Fanny呢?佢話05年兩個人做義工時識，仲好好傾，幾年來阿源都有掛住佢，不過始終唔敢搵對方，上年終於鼓起勇氣WhatsApp佢，阿源又爆金句話:「做男仔梗係要cool，唔可以做兵!」佢就send咗G.E.M.首《我的秘密》畀Fanny，叫佢留意歌詞示愛。之後約人行商場就拖手仔，話最鐘意Fanny夠真，又話覺得內涵係最重要嘅，所以女友個樣平凡就OK，就算畀嘉欣BB佢都唔要咁話!<br />\n<br />\n連登毒撚們打算等幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b53cb18b48be79268e0a08573c2b1b431e27863","tid":2487792,"uid":99700,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmbk6SkzHgXhbCGUxjw6w6ZwRyNvGgB6ngZz5GXv7CBgMa?filename=nceqgm7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnceqgm7.jpg&h=3f836d54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57a72dc710e46d911ecf539bb4b65de978a34a7f","tid":2487792,"uid":232466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:42:46.000Z","msg":"佢老婆咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8caa6c1989ca10f1a7fa954adee5bb030d8125","tid":2487792,"uid":381265,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:10:06.000Z","msg":"好人好姐叫 Fanny, 自己諗"},{"pid":"8232c5a7ee404bf098ea805745415fc1ea3f0837","tid":2487792,"uid":86246,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:11:46.000Z","msg":"連阿源自己都講佢個樣平凡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e73254b56a3116b67b7d505567c21dbeb8d1d8","tid":2487792,"uid":196181,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime